      • generateTorrentFromTfs

        public static List<com.turn.ttorrent.common.Torrent> generateTorrentFromTfs(File source,
                                                                            Encoding encoding,
                                                                            List<List<URI>> announceList,
                                                                            String createdBy,
                                                                            File cache,
                                                                            boolean link)
                                                                     throws InterruptedException,
                                                                            IOException
        Generate a list of torrent files for this tfs.
        Parameters:
        source - the root directory or file
        encoding - the encoding to use for nested torrents
        announceList - the announce list
        createdBy - creator signature
        cache - cache directory to initialize for seeding (null to skip)
        link - use symbolic links instead of copying to the cache directory
        Returns:
        the list of torrent files
        Throws:
        InterruptedException
        IOException
